{
  "stem": "13457.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my understanding was that they were taking hostages, because they didn't want, so to speak, any disturbance during the Polish day of independence.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "As it is, of course, my father wasn't then in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He, by that time, was on the eastern part of Poland with my aunt, which was already at that time occupied by, by Russians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So they looked for my father in the bedroom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then something moved under the quilt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was my chihuahua, my little doggy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And first they saw that somebody's hiding there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But then they realized there was a dog.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So anyway, they walked away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And-- but at that time, my understanding is that my uncle in, in Lodz was taken as hostage.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he was shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And in other words, he-- they, they were shooting these hostages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So it was luck that my father wasn't already there in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "From the understanding gained after the war, the way the statement by my father goes, he understood what was coming.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he promised himself-- or promised my mother, too-- that the Germans would never take him alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So he apparently comprehended the dangers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And that's why he wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Anyway, he was then, as I mentioned before, in the eastern Poland when the Russians walked in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they were sorting out, when the Russians came, between the officers and the enlisted men.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "My father was an officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He was clever enough to, to realize that when the Russians are dividing between the officers and non-officers, there will be no, no good coming out of this, particularly to the Polish officers.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "He was one of the few, if I may say from my understanding now, Jews that were in-- were officers in Polish army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Anyway, he quit, then, that group.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
